{"type": "article", "id": 25956, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-26T07:35:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26716, "name": "OPLØFT"}, {"id": 26717, "name": "Ulisse"}, {"id": 26718, "name": "Bump"}, {"id": 26719, "name": "Markus Johansson Design Studio"}, {"id": 26720, "name": "Moore + Giles"}, {"id": 26721, "name": "Savon Stories"}, {"id": 26722, "name": "Menta"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}, {"id": 6594, "name": "Karim Rashid"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140244dpbIlHiR6CUhYV5B.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Carronade Lamps by Markus Johansson Design Studio</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.leklint.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Le Klint</a> 旗下的这组看上去像专业摄影棚内照明的灯具系列名叫 Carronade，由 <a href=\"http://markusjohansson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Markus Johansson Design Studio</a> 设计。这一系列灯具包括：落地灯、桌灯和小型装饰灯，黑色的金属支架搭配胡桃木和黄铜组件。时尚大方的外型无论是在办公还是居家场所都非常适用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071816395O42dUTsX80f6Zjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181639wdyuvSYKONpGD2FQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181640hg01M45pF9fxmwWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.66166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181640f1H3vLZchbQktS78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181641Zs71pfJCxBhALt63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181641Sec4AFNxtQsyD103.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>OPLØFT by OPLØFT team</h2>\n<p class=\"\">想避免久坐的办公方式苦于找不到好的办法？这款名叫 <a href=\"http://oploft.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OPLØFT</a> 的工作桌可以让你轻松调节高度，站着办公。这个由丹麦的一个小团队所设计的工作桌可以很好地契合在已有的办公桌面上，外型流露着北欧的精简。它的重量约为 12 千克，最大承重为 40 千克，最高可抬升 40 厘米的高度。如果你对这款工作桌感兴趣，可以在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/584258111/oplft-make-your-desk-height-adjustable\">Kickstarter</a> 上参与众筹。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181642g1JChIAXU3LVwdTR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181644vTrOC7ZgDep5U60N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181644cSQysL5gipVKYtJl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181645ugdULwNqSXW9RJ7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181645xrlD9cNeBmIWtRvL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Parker by Moore &amp; Giles</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.mooreandgiles.com/shop/parker-rolling-suitcase-baldwin/\">Parker</a> 的行李箱是美国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.mooreandgiles.com/\">Moore &amp; Giles</a> 的新品。行李箱外部采用的是天然的皮革，虽然外型简单但细节接缝处做工非常细腻，给人带来一种复古内敛的感觉。它有两个内部空间和四个拉链暗袋，售价为 1595 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181646CKjsoHX9aLlbN7Ur.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181646RrFg9f0ByMP78XpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071816470J4ZPhbcfjW1dNA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181647kVASJRm07ZtBjTPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071816480Un8mcruBTvJHO3D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Ulisse by Konstantin Grcic</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a href=\"http://konstantin-grcic.com/\">Konstantin Grcic</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.classicon.com/\">Classicon</a> 所设计的一款沙发床，名叫 Ulisse。它的基座由橡木和胡桃木制成，通过滚轴可以自由调节靠背角度。造型让人想起来自非洲和日本的美学设计，精简的同时强调着做工和材质的选择。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181648HxqEzyeQ3FcOg6Lr.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59413203\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181649D8QAWetjT1gGIFhN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181649WxGuo8wXKmLI5tAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78973105\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181650rhxgzTiuEqSoR3U6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62347188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181650oqtVkxGLpBN9mIr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78117359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Bump by Karim Rashid</h2>\n<p class=\"\">来自纽约的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/tag/karim-rashid/\">Karim Rashid</a> 带来了这款名为 Bump 的手机充电器，在不使用的情况下可以和收纳充电线（长 1 米）的中空圆环拼在一起，便于随身携带。充电器上的指示灯代表了剩余电量，它的开关是位于下方的圆形按钮。小巧的体积和明亮的颜色都是让人爱不释手的理由。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181651LKFBAY3Uz29tIZX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181651HmMWpJeDQNB8Ylrw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181651c3x71eglPsSGXKwf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181652wkaYCKdo8lZB4T1u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181652IupBjYoCF3KvqtO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Savon Stories by Menta</h2>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这是 <a href=\"http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.estudiomenta.mx%2F&amp;t=ZjQwNzRmYjQ1OWIwODk0ZTgwODAwYTVlMDA2MjMwNWU5MDZmMDk1NiwxdElIbkkyWQ%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">Menta</a> 为 Savon Stories 新的沐浴皂系列所设计的包装，清新细腻的插画表现了四种不同的香型，仿佛取自某个植物学家精心绘制的笔记。最外一圈品牌标签组成的系带是这款包装的点睛之笔，给人感觉像是打开了一个充满夏日气息的礼物盒。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181653BXTcSkbr7nNli0qZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181653JmCQuoYMw9850X6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181654CIc0aY83qy72pGJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181655TmH4fUAOjJXz6olS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181655thY6sV1Jjei5WqXl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181656LtE7ZNnwvoDJefsC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}